strings: <voice_0x010018ED><se_def>Dhoulmagus: Do you think perhaps...you could teach me some magic soon?

<voice_0x010018EE><se_low>Rylus: Not this again, Dhoulmagus.
You are not yet ready.
As I have said many times before.

<voice_0x010018EF><se_low>Rylus: What about your chores, hm?
Have you finished clearing up outside?

<voice_0x010018F1><se_low>Rylus: Well don't just stand there!
Get on with it!
<voice_0x010018F3><se_low>Rylus: Hm, there's still something missing. But what? I'm so close now. So very close...
